description: The fund invests primarily in equity securities of mid-cap growth companies with an environmental, social and governance (“ESG”) rating of medium or better, as rated by Sustainalytics, a third-party ESG rating agency, at the time of purchase. Under normal circumstances, 80% of companies in the fund’s portfolio, based on net assets, will have a Sustainalytics ESG rating. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Alger Weatherbie Enduring Growth ETF
